              </a>
            </p>
            <p class="date">November 1, 2022.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="blog-link">
            <p class="sub-title">So, you want to be a Software Developer?</p>
            <p class="title">
              <a
                href="https://medium.com/@victoria.mertens44/accelerated-learning-the-weekly-structure-68ca052c8044"
